dmca.title: ReviewsNest complains of copied piano lessons
dmca.body:
Hello Google,
 

I hereby bring to your attention an infringement of our copyrights published on blogspot.com.

http://www.reviewsnest.com/PianoLessons/index.htm 

2. The blog where my copyrighted work is published on is 
http://learn-piano-online.blogspot.com/2007/09/learn-to-play-piano-online19.html. It also appears under http://learn-piano-online.blogspot.com/2007/09/archive.html as the September 19 posting. 

3. Please contact me by email at [private]@reviewsnest.com, 
or via telephone at +[private].
